  "inter_chunk_silence_ms": 650,
  "chunks": [
    {
      "index": 0,
      "text": "Every A W S dev shipping with Claude knows this pain.",
      "checksum": "sha256:5d82fc72844bfccbe5e0d10074d056c14217b4a05fb08adc5ec5adbf95eda6d0",
      "wav": "chunk-00.wav",
      "duration": 3.01859410430839,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 0
    },
    {
      "index": 1,
      "text": "Bedrock gets the new features weeks late.",
      "checksum": "sha256:74d01948b59f7df43d845605800be9667b88e5f4cc286d8145c52dcb4382a26f",
      "wav": "chunk-01.wav",
      "duration": 2.2291156462585033,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 11
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "text": "But today, that lag is gone. Anthropic just shipped the full Claude Platform on A W S.",
      "checksum": "sha256:56c96ed781a446fe0ab3797a4a5052d54e8f201d44eeb818753e9b3d1708e41e",
      "wav": "chunk-02.wav",
      "duration": 5.108390022675737,
      "word_count": 17,
      "words_offset": 18
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "text": "Generally available today. And here's the part most people will miss.",
      "checksum": "sha256:1c6bb5ac99c731f46a4bfc9e3fec36d28a27bb1150a54e2e4939a0cbf301e1ca",
      "wav": "chunk-03.wav",
      "duration": 3.7151927437641725,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 35
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "text": "This is not Bedrock with a new name. Bedrock is the data-resident subset.",
      "checksum": "sha256:14eb5486f4b72fcc6ca93b701c21839582871044980e53700909d956d8e28b76",
      "wav": "chunk-04.wav",
      "duration": 4.458231292517007,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 46
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "text": "Platform-on-A W S is the full native A P I.",
      "checksum": "sha256:3d976e0299293cdc4cb9a50fee93c909e511cfd0b8477c1b64ac73214524bedc",
      "wav": "chunk-05.wav",
      "duration": 3.3436734693877552,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 59
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "text": "Day zero. Which means the entire beta surface lands on A W S today.",
      "checksum": "sha256:da5d9f4be35b7e4bfb5c291fb8a44e3b6d06de3dd54b2fa9bf00f144bafcaa09",
      "wav": "chunk-06.wav",
      "duration": 4.876190476190477,
      "word_count": 14,
      "words_offset": 69
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "text": "Managed Agents. Advisor. Skills. Files. M C P connector.",
      "checksum": "sha256:bf8d94a72d9bf306390b797e9e2fe9afc4f7df00d822edce79d71892254d5646",
      "wav": "chunk-07.wav",
      "duration": 3.900952380952381,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 83
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "text": "Code execution. Web search. And the Claude Console, on A W S for the first time.",
      "checksum": "sha256:2f1c9ba2a2fa95408cda82b08979d423fe286e17c444de3ee2da2ca3b16400b4",
      "wav": "chunk-08.wav",
      "duration": 5.294149659863946,
      "word_count": 16,
      "words_offset": 92
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "text": "The prompt improver, the generator, the evals U I.",
      "checksum": "sha256:468d881bf5e40876eedea30825e875c946f7c05c3ced9a06f47f8127594dd3f2",
      "wav": "chunk-09.wav",
      "duration": 3.297233560090703,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 108
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "text": "And here's how it ships through your A W S account.",
      "checksum": "sha256:348953c5793ce0a08e579f29cd499d8229ef96dde9ed28e1b5b4eb61df2392d7",
      "wav": "chunk-10.wav",
      "duration": 3.111473922902494,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 117
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "text": "The endpoint runs on A W S external anthropic dot region dot A P I dot A W S.",
      "checksum": "sha256:fef5ad0248955bf0f8333783bc75684f9120cbc98f782459916499095d7a5b68",
      "wav": "chunk-11.wav",
      "duration": 5.758548752834467,
      "word_count": 19,
      "words_offset": 128
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "text": "Auth is through Identity Access Management.",
      "checksum": "sha256:0b1313682bb15da69d3076ab98c95da4224776e192df4d94aa5f7a3c8f5f6352",
      "wav": "chunk-12.wav",
      "duration": 2.414875283446712,
      "word_count": 6,
      "words_offset": 147
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "text": "Every call is a CloudTrail event. Billing rides on A W S Marketplace, retiring against your existing commitment.",
      "checksum": "sha256:14d7c0856dfc895aec1fb014859b35fed5ce695fc275c4b5648943671ded46e4",
      "wav": "chunk-13.wav",
      "duration": 6.780226757369615,
      "word_count": 18,
      "words_offset": 153
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "text": "Plus, it's available in eighteen A W S regions at G A.",
      "checksum": "sha256:7feb309410ce5f936e44ee09184b13557572005bf9f04b631585b8870b9cfaf4",
      "wav": "chunk-14.wav",
      "duration": 3.575873015873016,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 171
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "text": "That's broader than most Claude routes at launch.",
      "checksum": "sha256:fbb5da49b7cbaad18e47e3ddbc96ec547039ccb19797afc851a5385e5ca86708",
      "wav": "chunk-15.wav",
      "duration": 2.461315192743764,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 183
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "text": "Three named customers are already shipping on it.",
      "checksum": "sha256:6a41f3642653d06e9977be0eec9778f0d4b9058d075fcf74e47cec2bb508e7db",
      "wav": "chunk-16.wav",
      "duration": 2.461315192743764,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 191
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "text": "ReliaQuest in cybersecurity. OpenRouter routing through A W S Identity Access Management.",
      "checksum": "sha256:30581976e7edadabff59adcdb74cdf93581862b7ae8337b42617b4b0a08479ae",
      "wav": "chunk-17.wav",
      "duration": 6.176507936507937,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 199
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "text": "And Emergent, with day-one access to every new model.",
      "checksum": "sha256:baf113a4c704c762f06a32bf21f2d32257316bd99f339b4aeebdda5f55085c87",
      "wav": "chunk-18.wav",
      "duration": 3.1579138321995464,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 211
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "text": "So when do you pick which? If you want every beta from day one, that's Platform-on-A W S.",
      "checksum": "sha256:db3de9146bdfce59c70fca323b8931d40ee23c48a866e5f727bb9d578c6b4423",
      "wav": "chunk-19.wav",
      "duration": 5.340589569160998,
      "word_count": 18,
      "words_offset": 220
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "text": "If your data must stay inside A W S, that's Bedrock.",
      "checksum": "sha256:ab24796bc3b0452e46179ec57742a7dc210107204d2a83fa0bd26023fa94388b",
      "wav": "chunk-20.wav",
      "duration": 3.3901133786848074,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 238
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "text": "The version lag is over. Is this the end of Bedrock for new agents?",
      "checksum": "sha256:10f4ecc56e46e816932f67044c4b9b04aa45a83314944215660a48dad7645f41",
      "wav": "chunk-21.wav",
      "duration": 4.08671201814059,
      "word_count": 14,
      "words_offset": 249
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "text": "Tell me in the comments. Subscribe for more AI news.",
      "checksum": "sha256:769da9d3661d309be0ef01b1c5e827fce2b55e637580a9522c1fca9ebe72a223",
      "wav": "chunk-22.wav",
      "duration": 2.7399546485260773,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 263
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "text": "If you want to learn more about AI, check out the dynamous dot AI community.",
      "checksum": "sha256:ed8ab98bd7df91d3b58e78eff21993418ad4b085b0557e8f6564adfb92975283",
      "wav": "chunk-23.wav",
      "duration": 4.2260317460317465,
      "word_count": 15,
      "words_offset": 273
    }
  ]
}